model.implementation.occurrencesInformation

Class DesiredPopulationComposition

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.implementation.occurrencesInformation.DesiredPopulationComposition
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    EventRateTables, StatisticalTables, PopulationInformationCollection

    public class DesiredPopulationComposition
extends java.lang.Object
implements PopulationInformationCollection, EventRateTables, StatisticalTables
    The DesiredPopulationComposition holds data about the rate at which specified events occur to specified subsets of members of the summative population.
